            <p>Materials were acquired by the Hoover Institution Archives in 1974.</p>
        </acqinfo>
        <bioghist id="ref64">
            <head>Biographical/Historical note</head>
            <p>American journalist.</p>
        </bioghist>
        <scopecontent id="ref65">
            <head>Scope and Contents note</head>
            <p>Correspondence, writings, news dispatches, reports, bulletins, pamphlets, leaflets, clippings, computer disks, and photographs, relating to the Minutemen and other right-wing paramilitary groups in the United States, the Irish republican movement in Northern Ireland, and Islamic extremist movements. Video use copies of motion picture film available.</p>
        </scopecontent>
